  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "0ae30629bb0e1200e0c5adc714f19a5abc1e49d46044915ba0dc483e47fe6a87": "Oh, [?], you're back! I'm so glad. Did you manage to get the secateurs?",
    "1946c76a97f06b3797ead961d362cfb3c0e1a7ba0e2de4169aa07cec70e53578": "[?]! You found us! I'm so glad, I was afraid you wouldn't get my message.",
    "393617c3b8e5557006c5f4733a4ce4d44b50b738a60fd77f6a2412856971928f": "Hello [?]. How are you getting on with making that potion?",
    "400160aafbe218849147d2f6f89a6b932dd76f1b1baeeaafb567efee267624bf": "Hello [?], do you need any assistance?",
    "403d54cfcc0ca7dcbee52f863365835d2e27fe1c759386ad4de329aa615b17c3": "How's that potion of Magic Essence coming along, [?]?",
    "4aa0366cefbbeb0a9b719080bb3eddac6620b07e44c8c5fcd6964733c9dc9b89": "Pleased to meet you, [?]. As I was saying, I'm the healer in Zanaris. I graduated over 200 human years ago. Look, there's my Advanced Healing Certificate on the wall. I never go anywhere without it.",
    "897a579ea5d4f95d55b2d776794fb15332cc9b590c3c54d551cdd60c3ff61921": "Oh, [?] that's fantastic! Please give it to Her Majesty immediately.",
    "a5805ee0cc4fd89bc939a38dfbfbe9a364f4cb70448dd2776152d6b9a090704d": "I believe he now resides in the Dark Wizard's tower near Falador, and [?], please hurry. I fear the Queen doesn't have much time left!",
    "c693c0e9c7e451ccba382d507218092b0a7c7e41b980289be22bc57150ecd1e0": "Thank you, [?] but you'd better keep hold of it. You can't get to this hideout without it.",
    "c9f5caa511458fc43e204504158f413709ba4c2278f917ef7edda7c7d3f83b2c": "Oh, how rude of me! [?] this is Fairy Very Wise, advisor to the Queen. Fairy Very Wise, this is [?]."
  }
}